<p style="color:lightgray;font-size:14;">Rules:</p>
<p style="color:lightgray;font-size:14;">
The goal of the game is to eat weaker amoebas while running away from stronger
ones. When you eat a weaker amoeba you gain a level. If a stronger amoeba eats
you, you die. You win by gaining level 10.
<br><span style="color:white"><b>Controls: Arrow Keys or Numeric
Keypad. SPACE - skip a turn.</b></span><br>
<span style="color:yellow;font-size:14">
Turn <b>OFF</b> NumLock in Opera. Turn <b>ON</b>
NumLock in IE, Chromium.</span></p>

<p style="color:lightgray;font-size:14;">Map:</p>
<ul style="color:lightgray;font-size:14;">
<li><b>@</b> - you;
<li><b style="color:#707070">*</b> - impassable stone;
<li><b style="color:#00ff00">1</b> - <b style="color:#00ff00">9</b> - weak amoeba;
<li><b style="color:white">1</b> - <b style="color:white">9</b> - equal amoeba;
<li><b style="color:#ff0000">1</b> - <b style="color:#ff0000">9</b> - strong amoeba;
<li><b style="color:cyan">~</b> - dead amoeba;
</ul>

<p style="color:lightgray;font-size:14;">Notes:</p>
<ul style="color:lightgray;font-size:14;">
<li>amoebas are stupid and can't walk around stones;
<li>when eating weaker amoeba you gain a level;
<li>when stronger amoeba chews you, you die;
<li>you have a 66% chance of growing when eating amoeba of the same level;
<li>amoebas of the same level kill each other;
<li>amoebas of level 9 are always stronger than you;
</ul>

<p style="color:yellow;font-size:14">
Tested in Firefox 3, Opera 9, IE 6, Chromium.
</p>

